title: Product Pillage with Shuriken Shannon
description:
COMMENT ON THIS VIDEO ON STRANGENOTES.COM to win Shuriken's board shown in the video!

Ever wonder what it's like when your favorite pro goes to his sponsor's warehouse and raids the place for gear? Well now you can see exactly what it's like in this edition of Product Pillage on Strange Notes. Get possessed to skate and maybe you will be raiding the warehouse one day! Shuriken skates Santa Cruz Skateboards, Independent Trucks and OJ Wheels. 

Music: 
Lucas Perny and Miloslav Kollar
"The Har(l)em Shake" - The Rondel
